\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Independent Institute of Education \'28IIE\'29 is a private higher education Institution registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and also has programmes accredited by the CHE.\line \line The Institution is currently applying for the accreditation of a Bachelor of Arts in Copywriting programme which will be offered in a contact mode of delivery at the following campuses\'3A\line - Cape Town\'2C IIE Vega\'2C Cape Town \line - Durban\'2C IIE Vega\'2C Durban\line - Randburg\'2C IIE Vega\'2C Bordeaux\line - Pretoria\'2C IIE Vega\'2C Pretoria\line \line The Institution has also applied for the accreditation of a Bachelor of Arts.\line \line The Institution is accredited to offer the following programmes\'3A \line \line - Diploma in Integrated Brand Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts in Corporate Communication \line - Higher Certificate in Journalism \line - Diploma in Journalism Studies \line - Higher Certificate in Brand Building Practice \line - Master of Arts in Creative Brand Leadership \line - Bachelor of Arts in Strategic Brand Communication \line - Bachelor of Commerce in Strategic Brand Management \line - Advanced Diploma in Brand Innovation \line - Bachelor of Commerce Honours in Strategic Brand Management \line - Bachelor of Commerce Honours in Strategic Brand Management \line - Bachelor of Arts Honours in Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts in Strategic Brand Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts Honours in Strategic Brand Communication \line \line The IIE has the following programmes that are HEQSF-Aligned and deemed Accredited\'3A \line \line - Diploma in Integrated Brand Communications \line - Bachelor of Arts in Corporate Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts in Creative Brand Communication \line - Bachelor of Arts Honours in Communications Management\line \cell \pard 

